flowchart TD
    trigger([push / PR to master]) --> unit
    trigger --> integ

    subgraph unit[unit-tests job]
        u1[checkout + setup-dotnet 10] --> u2[install dotnet-coverage]
        u2 --> u3[collect -- dotnet test UnitTests]
        u3 --> u4[upload coverage-unit / unit.xml]
    end

    subgraph integ[integration-tests job]
        i1[docker compose up --build -d] --> i2{services healthy?\ncurl /Orders /Cart}
        i2 --> i3[dotnet test IntegrationTests NUnit HTTP]
        i3 --> i4[dotnet-coverage shutdown\norder-session / cart-session]
        i4 --> i5[compose down -> flush cobertura]
        i5 --> i6[stage order.xml + cart.xml]
        i6 --> i7[upload coverage-integration]
    end

    subgraph cont[inside each container]
        c1[PID1 dotnet-coverage collect] -->|spawns| c2[dotnet *.Web.dll]
        c3[CLR Profiler API] -.-> c1
        c2 -->|volume| c4[/coverage -> ./coverage-out/]
    end
    i1 -. starts .-> c1
    i4 -. shutdown .-> c1

    u4 --> report
    i7 --> report
    subgraph report[coverage-report job]
        r1[download coverage-*] --> r2[ReportGenerator merge\nunit+order+cart] --> r3[HTML + GitHub summary]
    end
